@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rerlyw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 + ((v1 + 0.21 - v2 + 0.03) / (v2 + 0.72 - v0 + 0.66)))
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.61)) / ((v2 + 0.70 + v2 + 0.89) - (v0 + 0.27 / v0 + 0.25)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v0)
    v1 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.23 / v1 + 0.05)) + wp.cos(0.19))
    data[tid] = v0
